{
  "schema": "2.0",
  "config": {
    "update_multi": true,
    "enable_forward": true,
    "width_mode": "fill"
  },
  "header": {
    "template": "blue",
    "title": {
      "tag": "plain_text",
      "content": "📖 __ARTICLE_TITLE__"
    },
    "subtitle": {
      "tag": "plain_text",
      "content": "__ARTICLE_SUBTITLE__"
    }
  },
  "body": {
    "direction": "vertical",
    "vertical_spacing": "medium",
    "elements": [
      {
        "tag": "markdown",
        "content": "**一句话摘要**：__TL_DR__\n\n<font color='grey'>原文链接</font>：[__ORIGIN_TITLE__](__ORIGIN_URL__)"
      },
      {
        "tag": "hr"
      },
      {
        "tag": "div",
        "fields": [
          {
            "is_short": true,
            "text": { "tag": "lark_md", "content": "**✍️ 作者**\n__AUTHOR__" }
          },
          {
            "is_short": true,
            "text": { "tag": "lark_md", "content": "**📅 发布**\n__PUBLISHED_AT__" }
          },
          {
            "is_short": true,
            "text": { "tag": "lark_md", "content": "**⏱ 阅读**\n__READ_TIME__" }
          },
          {
            "is_short": true,
            "text": { "tag": "lark_md", "content": "**🏷️ 分类**\n`__CATEGORY__`" }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "tag": "hr"
      },
      {
        "tag": "collapsible_panel",
        "expanded": true,
        "header": {
          "title": { "tag": "markdown", "content": "🎯 **核心观点**" },
          "background_color": "grey",
          "padding": "4px 8px 4px 8px",
          "icon": {
            "tag": "standard_icon",
            "token": "down-small-ccm_outlined",
            "size": "16px 16px"
          },
          "icon_position": "right",
          "icon_expanded_angle": -180
        },
        "elements": [
          {
            "tag": "markdown",
            "content": "- __POINT_1__\n- __POINT_2__\n- __POINT_3__"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "tag": "collapsible_panel",
        "expanded": true,
        "header": {
          "title": { "tag": "markdown", "content": "📊 **关键数据**" },
          "background_color": "grey",
          "padding": "4px 8px 4px 8px",
          "icon": {
            "tag": "standard_icon",
            "token": "down-small-ccm_outlined",
            "size": "16px 16px"
          },
          "icon_position": "right",
          "icon_expanded_angle": -180
        },
        "elements": [
          {
            "tag": "markdown",
            "content": "__KEY_METRIC_1__ 为 <font color='green'>__VALUE_1__</font>\n\n__KEY_METRIC_2__ 为 <font color='red'>__VALUE_2__</font>\n\n__KEY_METRIC_3__ 为 __VALUE_3__"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "tag": "collapsible_panel",
        "expanded": false,
        "header": {
          "title": { "tag": "markdown", "content": "💡 **深度解读（点击展开）**" },
          "background_color": "grey",
          "padding": "4px 8px 4px 8px",
          "icon": {
            "tag": "standard_icon",
            "token": "down-small-ccm_outlined",
            "size": "16px 16px"
          },
          "icon_position": "right",
          "icon_expanded_angle": -180
        },
        "elements": [
          {
            "tag": "markdown",
            "content": "__DEEP_ANALYSIS__（可放 200-500 字的深度解读，不用考虑长度，折叠面板本身就是藏次要信息）"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "tag": "collapsible_panel",
        "expanded": false,
        "header": {
          "title": { "tag": "markdown", "content": "🌟 **精彩引用（点击展开）**" },
          "background_color": "grey",
          "padding": "4px 8px 4px 8px",
          "icon": {
            "tag": "standard_icon",
            "token": "down-small-ccm_outlined",
            "size": "16px 16px"
          },
          "icon_position": "right",
          "icon_expanded_angle": -180
        },
        "elements": [
          {
            "tag": "markdown",
            "content": "> 「__QUOTE_1__」\n\n> 「__QUOTE_2__」"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "tag": "hr"
      },
      {
        "tag": "button",
        "text": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "📖 阅读原文" },
        "type": "primary",
        "width": "default",
        "behaviors": [
          { "type": "open_url", "default_url": "__ORIGIN_URL__" }
        ]
      },
      {
        "tag": "markdown",
        "text_size": "notation",
        "content": "<font color='grey'>📡 由 feishu-cli-card 技能生成 · 摘要基于原文整理</font>"
      }
    ]
  }
}
